highlights.text: “Sweater Weather” by The Neighbourhood has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 267 weeks straight.
“TIT FOR TAT” by Tate McRae is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #2.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “When Did You Get Hot?” is the highest at #9.
“Nice To Each Other” by Olivia Dean is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 110 spots at #70.
